SECTION D — HOW TO CITE
----------------------------------------------------------------------

To be advised...

If this repository supports a journal article or dataset DOI, please cite:

[YOUR NAME] ([YEAR]). “[ARTICLE / PROJECT TITLE].” [Journal/Outlet], [Volume(Issue)], [pages]. DOI: [DOI]
Repository: https://github.com/[OWNER]/[REPO]

Example BibTeX:
@misc{[yourkey],
  author       = {[YOUR NAME]},
  title        = {[ARTICLE / PROJECT TITLE]},
  year         = {[YEAR]},
  howpublished = {GitHub repository},
  url          = {https://github.com/[OWNER]/[REPO]},
  doi          = {[DOI]}
}

